'''百視達'''（{{lang-en|'''Blockbuster LLC'''}}），前稱：'''Blockbuster Entertainment Inc.'''）是一家[[美國|美國]]家庭影視娛樂供應商，最初只是出租錄像，後來發展到了[[串流媒體|串流媒體]]、[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]和影院等行業。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/news/ni0228635/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-01 |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408132006/http://www.imdb.com/news/ni0228635/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

在其2004年發展高峰時段，擁有超過六萬名員工和九千家商店。<ref>{{cite news|title=15 Companies That Might Not Survive 2009|url=http://money.usnews.com/money/blogs/flowchart/2009/2/6/15-companies-that-might-not-survive-2009.html|author=Rick Newman|date=February 6, 2009|accessdate=December 9, 2010|publisher=US News|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205145626/http://money.usnews.com/money/blogs/flowchart/2009/2/6/15-companies-that-might-not-survive-2009.html|archivedate=2010年12月5日}}</ref><ref name= nyt09>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/09/business/09blockbuster.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-01 |archive-date=2014-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128034218/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/09/business/09blockbuster.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

因為隨著2010年代數位化電影的興起，實體出租商店逐漸倒閉的情況下，百視達在與競爭對手[[Netflix|Netflix]]和Redbox的交鋒中失利，於2010年9月23日[[破產|破產]]。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Blockbuster Reaches Agreement on Plan to Recapitalize Balance Sheet and Substantially Reduce its Indebtedness |publisher=Blockbuster |date=September 23, 2010 |url=http://blockbuster.mediaroom.com/index.php?s=119&item=929 |accessdate=2010-09-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100927030831/http://blockbuster.mediaroom.com/index.php?s=119&item=929 |archivedate=2010年9月27日 |df= }}</ref> 

2011年4月6日，百視達和所剩下1,700家商店被[[Dish_Network|Dish Network]]以2.33億美元的價格買下，並由後者負擔其8700萬美元的債務。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/07/business/la-fi-ct-dish-blockbuster-20110407 |title=Dish Network wins bidding for assets of bankrupt Blockbuster |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2011-05-02 |first=Ben |last=Fritz |date=April 7, 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421034918/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/07/business/la-fi-ct-dish-blockbuster-20110407 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在隨後的幾年中Dish Network逐漸關閉了上千家百視達的商店，<ref>{{cite web |last=Flacy |first=Mike |url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/home-theater/dish-network-shutting-down-a-third-of-all-remaining-blockbuster-stores/ |title=Dish Network shutting down a third of all remaining Blockbuster stores |publisher=Digital Trends |date=2012-02-23 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101011502/http://www.digitaltrends.com/home-theater/dish-network-shutting-down-a-third-of-all-remaining-blockbuster-stores/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://money.msn.com/top-stocks/post.aspx?post=e4ad0423-bd75-4a2c-a689-2837c7ae6729 |title=More Blockbuster stores closing |publisher=MSN Money |date=2012-02-23 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925001318/http://money.msn.com/top-stocks/post.aspx?post=e4ad0423-bd75-4a2c-a689-2837c7ae6729 |archive-date=2014-09-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Pankratz |first=Howard |url=http://www.denverpost.com/ci_22419439/dish-close-300-blockbuster-stores |title=Dish to close 300 Blockbuster stores |publisher=The Denver Post |date= |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109083715/http://www.denverpost.com/ci_22419439/dish-close-300-blockbuster-stores |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

2013年11月宣佈將關閉剩餘的300家商店，該公司的郵寄錄像服務也將停止運營。<ref>{{cite web |author=By Patrick deHahn |url=http://money.cnn.com/2013/11/06/news/companies/blockbuster-stores-closing/ |title=Blockbuster to shutter all U.S. stores |publisher=Money.CNN.com |date=November 6, 2013 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2013-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107085416/http://money.cnn.com/2013/11/06/news/companies/blockbuster-stores-closing/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Blockbuster Closures: Dish Network To Shutter 300 Video Stores In U.S., Lay Off 3,000 Workers ">{{cite web | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/01/22/blockbuster-closures-dish-network_n_2523618.html | title=Blockbuster Closures: Dish Network To Shutter 300 Video Stores In U.S., Lay Off 3,000 Workers | publisher=AP via Huffington Post | date=2013-01-21 | accessdate=7 November 2013 | archive-date=2013-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131116063116/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/01/22/blockbuster-closures-dish-network_n_2523618.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2016年，一名男子於Cybernight报告说，12家特许经营的Blockbuster商店在美国运营。<ref name="IsntDead">{{cite web |title=The Blockbuster Fan Page |url=http://cybernight.elementfx.com/buster.html |accessdate=2016-10-24 |archive-date=2016-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024000222/http://cybernight.elementfx.com/buster.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年，百視達宣布將美國位於安克拉治的兩家分店關閉。<ref>{{cite web|title=美「百視達」昔近萬店 如今剩1家|url=https://udn.com/news/story/11316/3252993|accessdate=2018-07-15|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715094020/https://udn.com/news/story/11316/3252993|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年3月底，百視達位於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[伯斯|伯斯]]的分店宣布關閉。全世界僅存最後一家分店位於[[美國|美國]][[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]本得市，2019年3月上映的[[漫威电影宇宙|漫威]]電影《[[驚奇隊長_(電影)|驚奇隊長]]》，其中有电影场景就在此店拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|title=Australia’s last Blockbuster store in Morley, WA closing its doors|url=https://thewest.com.au/business/retail/australias-last-blockbuster-store-in-morley-wa-closing-its-doors-ng-b881122768z|publisher=The West Australian|date=1 March 2019|accessdate=2019-03-06|archive-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624170303/https://thewest.com.au/business/retail/australias-last-blockbuster-store-in-morley-wa-closing-its-doors-ng-b881122768z|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==百視達香港==
1999年，美國百視達從破產管理官收購金獅部份分店，繼續經營。曾由19間分店擴充至24間。但在盜版問題，與[[VCD|VCD]]、[[DVD|DVD]]影碟銷售逐漸盛行等情況下，百視達亦在2004年逐漸結業，全面撤出香港。<ref>[http://appledaily.atnext.com/template/apple/art_main.cfm?iss_id=20040130&sec_id=4104&subsec_id=11867&art_id=3823987 七店已關閉 200員工失業 百視達分段結業影響20萬客戶]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} 蘋果日報，2004年1月30日</ref> 百視達結業前，在香港擁有24間分店，約有20萬會員。

==百視達台灣==
2007年，[[中興保全|中興保全]]成立「樂到家國際娛樂股份有限公司」，總部位於台北市大同區鄭州路139號7樓（國產實業大樓），正式取得百視達在台灣的總代理及擁有100%股權。台灣百視達於2013年改為「樂到家」（[[英語|英語]]：LOTS HOME）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120910/100740.htm|title=台灣百視達改名「樂到家」　原店會員權益不變|date=2012-09-01|publisher=[[ETtoday新聞雲|ETtoday新聞雲]]|accessdate=2020-05-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916124916/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120910/100740.htm|archivedate=2017-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而後在2017年8月結束所有直營門市，轉型電影內容提供商<ref>
{{cite news|url=https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=279201|title=時代眼淚！「樂到家」直營門市將收攤　影視出租店恐成歷史|date=2017-08-02|publisher=[[三立新聞網|三立新聞網]]|accessdate=2020-05-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812174515/https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=279201|archivedate=2017-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

